\033[1m\033[32mEDIT\033[0m - Edit a script in the current mango repository

\033[1mUSAGE:\033[0m
    mango @edit [script_name]

\033[1mDESCRIPTION:\033[0m
    Opens an existing script in the default editor for editing.
    The script must exist in the current mango repository.
    If the script does not exist, an error will be raised.

\033[1mARGUMENTS:\033[0m
    script_name    Name of the script to edit

\033[1mEXAMPLES:\033[0m
    mango @edit myscript
    mango @edit existing-script